045300     MOVE "TEST(S) DELETED     " TO ENDER-DESC.                   OBNC14.2
045400     MOVE CCVS-E-2 TO DUMMY-RECORD. PERFORM WRITE-LINE.           OBNC14.2
045500      IF   INSPECT-COUNTER EQUAL TO ZERO                          OBNC14.2
