040200     MOVE CCVS-E-3 TO DUMMY-RECORD. PERFORM WRITE-LINE.           OBSQ34.2
040300 WRITE-LINE.                                                      OBSQ34.2
040400     ADD 1 TO RECORD-COUNT.                                       OBSQ34.2
040500     IF RECORD-COUNT GREATER 50                                   OBSQ34.2
